script.script:
/**Conditional
DDuoDialingCondRule

The attribute must be saved in the catalog only if the related attribute assumes the value shown in the column H.

Duo
DuoDialing

Duo
ApplyShortDialing

TRUE
*/

var entity=data.Duo;

if(entity.DuoDialing && !entity.ApplyShortDialing      )
{
